Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.51,0:01:11.65,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上双眼用心去感受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:18.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,满溢的热气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:22.81,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,答案就在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:29.70,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那一日的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:32.65,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,并非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.97,0:01:38.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,苏醒的追忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:41.92,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,katharsis
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:47.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,解放吧 将一切解放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:50.05,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着未来跑动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:53.03,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,名为青涩和你的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.03,0:01:55.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,现在立刻就传达到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:58.41,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,强而有力地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:03.38,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,朝那倾洒而出的光芒 伸出双手
